    "notes": [
      "Phase 4 Step 5a: this file ships tier metadata ONLY. The loader does NOT yet read the tier or openEvent fields. V1 behavior is unchanged.",
      "tier values: L0 (BootKernel) | L1 (EarlyFoundation) | L2 (SurfaceCritical) | L3 (RouteAware) | L4 (IdleHydration default) | L5 (OnDemand) | L6 (Visibility/Gesture) | DebugOnly.",
      "Any alias not listed in 'scripts' below defaults to L4 with no openEvent.",
      "openEvent is only meaningful for L5 (and conceptually L6); listed here for forward compatibility. Empty/absent means no on-demand trigger.",
      "L0/L1 must remain a small kernel allowlist. The validator may warn if a non-allowlisted alias appears at L0/L1."
    ],
